{"type": "article", "id": 3319, "title": "陶瓷炊具", "description": "", "date": "2014-11-06T08:02:47Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 3, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605233014A8ti4aHU5h2ZEzds.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t日本 Japan Suite 公司最近邀请陶瓷艺术家 Kodo Kiyooka 将精美的陶瓷艺术品变成了日常生活所用的炊具，推出了一套包括煎锅、碗、咖啡壶、杯子等在内的陶瓷炊具。Kodo Kiyooka 一直擅于将艺术融入日常生活用品的设计，他选择了棕褐色的稻草灰制成的面釉与各种火山灰与矿物质混合而成的瓷蓝灰釉材质。这套炊具视觉上给人分量很重的感觉，但其实它非常轻巧，可以说是对耐用度与便捷程度做了很好的结合。定价 60 至 210 美元，<a href=\"http://www.japan-suite.com/\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里尝试购买</a>。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233011T3NuI0UYLbC6ndza.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.7515625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233012yldZD61N275q8OA9.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.665625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233012iHBaU54cS8rPu9eD.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.665625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233013sbmxLhJy9wHYoMqZ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.665625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233013zgNuh41roZ2W35wt.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.665625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<br>\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n\t<br>\r\n</div>\n\n\n"}